Package: excelerate
Type: Package
Title: Functions to Create and Export Excel Spreadsheets for Supplementary Tables
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Amelia", "Edmondson-Stait",
      email = "aedmond3@ed.ac.uk",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: The **excellerate** package provides a set of functions to easily create 
    and export Excel spreadsheets, specifically for generating supplementary 
    tables required when preparing research manuscripts for scientific journals. 
    It allows for quick and customizable table creation from R data, making it 
    easier to structure and format tables according to journal requirements.
